---
title: Saucy Chermoula Beef with Green Beans & Jewelled Couscous | Serves 2
description: Time for another meal-prep masterpiece! We've got a fluffy carrot and currant-speckled couscous, crisp green beans and
coconutty, chermoula-spiced beef strips, all packed up and ready to go! Pop it in the microwave and dig in.
